{"tid":1212475,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"[購物指南] 如何選購有用既口罩去防催淚彈","createTime":"2019-06-12T18:56:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T12:02:49.000Z","uid":76413,"like":51,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"00cfebe2931ce23314b166c2d4927cdde31c6c28","tid":1212475,"uid":76413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:56:43.000Z","msg":"先講結論：最差 N100 &lt; R100 &lt; P100 最好<br />\n<br />\n係用口罩前要先了解到催淚彈究竟係乜野<br />\n<a href=\"https://pansci.asia/archives/68262\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpansci.asia%2Farchives%2F68262&d=0lytrcPBTEnksf4YR0ybMQRUsGYs0X8VP9vM6mjQjJM%3D&h=4f286687\" target=\"_blank\">https://pansci.asia/archives/68262</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">催淚彈組成</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">其實催淚彈的組成並不是全都是為了催淚，主要分三種目的：加溫、散佈、催淚。歷史最悠久的催淚成分有三種：溴化二甲苯（Xylyl bromide）、2-氯苯乙酮（Phenacyl chloride，簡稱CN）、鄰-氯代苯亞甲基丙二腈（2-chlorobenzalmalononitrile，簡稱CS），其中CN毒性最強，所以大多已經被CS取代用於鎮暴的催淚彈 [4]。除了CS，1962年意外被合成出來的CR（Dibenz[b,f][1,4]oxazepine）也有用於催淚彈；不過和CS不同，CS容易用水去除，但CR遇水反而會加劇作用，是比較危險的成分。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，催淚的CS在常溫下是固體粉末。為了要讓CS能夠像氣體一樣散佈，就需要加入其他成分－像是容易揮發的二氯甲烷，讓它帶著CS擴散在空氣中。除此之外，高溫也有助於氣體散佈，所以催淚彈也會加入其他的化學物質來產生溫度，加速CS的擴散，這也是為什麼上街示威教學都會提到不要徒手撿起剛落地的催淚彈，很可能因此燙傷。 </span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">多得以前熱狗上過報，我地可以知道香港係用CS</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/1/1b/Gren_Hand_Burst_Irrt-_A.Riot-_N225.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F1%2F1b%2FGren_Hand_Burst_Irrt-_A.Riot-_N225.jpg&h=10a72355&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後我地市面上可以搵到既口罩一般係跟NIOSH(美國國家職業安全衛生研究所)既標準<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cdc.gov/niosh/npg/pgintrod.html#nrp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fniosh%2Fnpg%2Fpgintrod.html%23nrp&d=0lytrcPBTEnksf4YR0ybMQRUsGYs0X8VP9vM6mjQjJM%3D&h=cdb872ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cdc.gov/niosh/npg/pgintrod.html#nrp</a><br />\n呢度講得好清楚<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">P同R都防油，但R級只有約8個鐘效用，P就冇限制\nN就不防油</code></pre><br />\n理論上而言我地唔會接觸到油性微粒，但唔肯定胡椒噴霧有冇<br />\n所以P同R級優先考慮<br />\n<br />\n然後到型號<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cdc.gov/niosh/npg/npgd0122.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fniosh%2Fnpg%2Fnpgd0122.html&d=0lytrcPBTEnksf4YR0ybMQRUsGYs0X8VP9vM6mjQjJM%3D&h=69b33e1d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cdc.gov/niosh/npg/npgd0122.html</a><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">Up to 2 mg/m3: \n(APF = 25) Any supplied-air respirator operated in a continuous-flow mode&pound;\n(APF = 50) Any air-purifying, full-facepiece respirator (gas mask) with a chin-style, front- or back-mounted canister providing protection against the compound of concern and having an N100, R100, or P100 filter. \nClick here for information on selection of N, R, or P filters.\n(APF = 50) Any self-contained breathing apparatus with a full facepiece\n(APF = 50) Any supplied-air respirator with a full facepiece</code></pre><br />\n就3種N100, R100, P100<br />\nN95係防唔晒，所以先有巴打會聞到仲有味<br />\n唔好入錯其他，好多口罩係防其他野(如VOCs之類)<br />\n<br />\n同埋口罩有分幾種，好似外科口罩咁既垃圾平面式、N95款既防護型口罩同埋豬咀口罩<br />\n例如P100都有N95咁樣既，同埋豬咀口罩版濾綿<br />\n外科口罩<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.jianqun.com.tw/uploads/info/0303-1.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jianqun.com.tw%2Fuploads%2Finfo%2F0303-1.JPG&h=b3b7d06a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nN95<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.mediequip.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B-3M-8210-N95-%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mediequip.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B-3M-8210-N95-%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9.jpg&h=599152e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n豬咀口罩(P100濾綿)<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/81U1ISyvPKL._SX466_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-na.ssl-images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FI%2F81U1ISyvPKL._SX466_.jpg&h=aa8463f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n豬咀口罩全部都有頭罩扣住所以係唔會點甩<br />\nN95款撞到係會移位入氣既<br />\n但留意返N95款同豬咀都焗到仆街<br />\n所以最好都有個外科口罩平時用<br />\n狗衝時先去用N100, R100, P100<br />\n<br />\n以上呢堆新填地街比較易搵<br />\n祝身體健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2f996be59b0597074587bd06a0da70ffac3bce6","tid":1212475,"uid":76413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T19:02:57.000Z","msg":"屌開錯台<br />\n留意返催淚的CS係粉狀<br />\n如果件衫中左記得要分開手洗<br />\n唔係有機會搞到其他衫"},{"pid":"5ecb8234038da9c17f0146ab46187bbd72cd24bc","tid":1212475,"uid":78300,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T19:20:26.000Z","msg":"整合左做短既msg 大家可以幫手share出去嘛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家可能未必敢衝，唔敢整武器驚班狗升級武力<br />\n但係大家可以學整盾牌，而唔係用頭盔 水樽 遮 去硬食班狗既攻擊<br />\n基本上 盾可以擋到膠子彈 警棍 部分既傷害 唔洗硬食曬<br />\n<br />\n唔敢衝既你亦都可以係後方整盾 保護好前線 減低傷亡 我地先至贏到架<br />\n整盾可以保護到大家 又唔會話比藉口班狗升級武力<br />\n<br />\n大家一齊spread 開佢 唔好再硬食傷害啦 班狗越嚟越狼死架啦<br />\n<br />\n40秒開始睇製作<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0pAea8o__b8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0pAea8o__b8&d=0lytrcPBTEnksf4YR0ybMQRUsGYs0X8VP9vM6mjQjJM%3D&h=200be955\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0pAea8o__b8</a>"},{"pid":"31ffbf67adac38d0af61a64ce24989f7f251f24a","tid":1212475,"uid":57868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T19:23:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"03a93afb20e820ef0b92f9b561d9f9366e0adbe7","tid":1212475,"uid":57868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T19:23:30.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e297c663e05303c42bf2d341c52302214dfc6c07","tid":1212475,"uid":53481,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T19:25:36.000Z","msg":"剛剛訂咗一大堆N95，咁洗唔洗cancel?"},{"pid":"4c5e6992c6ea120018df735cb08dca90052f8de2","tid":1212475,"uid":76413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e297c663e05303c42bf2d341c52302214dfc6c07","tid":1212475,"uid":53481,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T19:25:36.000Z","msg":"剛剛訂咗一大堆N95，咁洗唔洗cancel?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T19:28:48.000Z","msg":"你睇下搵唔搵到代替品先<br />\n冇都冇計"},{"pid":"d700da6b6ec6052eef645e872b68c57e4916f15c","tid":1212475,"uid":191846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T19:29:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"55030e773986df9986482fc8803245de16d852f7","tid":1212475,"uid":222809,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T19:30:50.000Z","msg":"夢見有人將油漆倒入氣球裡面 好似水彈咁拋出去 爆開個下好靚 五顏六色 遍地開花嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後就成為左香港新地標：藝術夏慤道～"},{"pid":"429333ed55294cd9f6e5ef4a3242baf3eaf98794","tid":1212475,"uid":76413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T01:33:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a8649cffcd8cfd67377d332fbc2c8e3a8056f56a","tid":1212475,"uid":76413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:00:45.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"53c06d239d51deeb932512e3fbfcb949c5d95b4f","tid":1212475,"uid":76413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:12:46.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"cce444234259e3eb08934f1b0b4bd2009346664b","tid":1212475,"uid":76413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:35:36.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"95a0779db43c561d77126da24de6f18f1ddbc2bf","tid":1212475,"uid":76413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:35:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8694029c981a4fdab63fb10c69230e592fd56cd8","tid":1212475,"uid":202094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:42:18.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4981b4b5922b27728cc5dbf92d8f8773aa6d2214","tid":1212475,"uid":202094,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:44:38.000Z","msg":"個人經驗 真心覺得用防毒口罩好重要 物資站多數都係普通口罩 