,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:47:47.000Z","msg":"普通口罩防比人點相<br />\n開拖先戴防毒<br />\n<br />\n平時都戴防毒焗撚死你"},{"pid":"f764bfe4a030c3cc0c6a27a6ee7e657d8c1794a7","tid":1212475,"uid":76413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:50:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1214624/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1214624/page/1</a><br />\n推呢個好少少"},{"pid":"a7ecfbc30b98303d6e6861ccbfcc02cb06948ff6","tid":1212475,"uid":137783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T08:04:51.000Z","msg":"好po無人推？"}]}